---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Disclaimer - OPTYP" 
  description="Legal Disclaimer for OPTYP – covering service limitations, professional advice, third-party links, and liability terms.">

  <section class="relative py-20 px-6 bg-gradient-to-br from-black via-gray-900 to-black text-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-4xl font-body">

      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold mb-4 text-white">Disclaimer</h1>
        <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-400 to-green-500 mx-auto mb-8 rounded-full shadow-sm"></div>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          This Disclaimer outlines the limitations of OPTYP’s responsibilities and ensures transparency regarding the use of our website, services, and information provided.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-400">
          Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <article class="prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none space-y-12 text-gray-300">

        <!-- General Information -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-teal-400 font-bold text-2xl mb-4">1. General Information</h2>
          <div class="glass-box p-6 rounded-xl">
            <p>
              The content and services provided by OPTYP are intended for general informational and professional assistance purposes only. 
              We make no guarantees regarding career success, job placement, or interview results based on our services or materials.
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Professional Advice -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-teal-400 font-bold text-2xl mb-4">2. Professional Advice Disclaimer</h2>
          <p>
            OPTYP does not offer legal, financial, or psychological advice. Any career-related advice, suggestions, or examples shared through our services are 
            based on general professional experience and are not to be considered as formal guidance or guarantees.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-gray-400 text-sm">
            Always consult a qualified professional before making major career or financial decisions.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Career Outcome Disclaimer -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-teal-400 font-bold text-2xl mb-4">3. Career Outcomes</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>OPTYP does not guarantee job placements, interviews, or promotions.</li>
            <li>Results depend on market conditions, employer preferences, and user effort.</li>
            <li>Our services are designed to enhance presentation and visibility, not to influence hiring decisions.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <!-- Accuracy of Information -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-teal-400 font-bold text-2xl mb-4">4. Accuracy of Information</h2>
          <p>
            While we strive for accuracy and timeliness, OPTYP does not warrant that all website information, tools, or materials are error-free, complete, or current. 
            Any reliance on provided content is at your own discretion.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Third-Party Links -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-teal-400 font-bold text-2xl mb-4">5. Third-Party Links & Services</h2>
          <p>
            Our website may contain links to third-party platforms (e.g., LinkedIn, Naukri, Fiverr). These are provided solely for convenience and informational purposes. 
            OPTYP does not endorse, monitor, or control the content or privacy practices of external websites.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-gray-400 text-sm">
            You are encouraged to review the privacy policies of all third-party sites before engaging with them.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Testimonials Disclaimer -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-teal-400 font-bold text-2xl mb-4">6. Testimonials Disclaimer</h2>
          <p>
            Testimonials featured on our website or social media platforms represent real customer experiences but are individual in nature. 
            Outcomes and satisfaction levels may vary depending on user engagement and external factors.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Limitation of Liability -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-teal-400 font-bold text-2xl mb-4">7. Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <div class="glass-box p-6 rounded-xl border border-red-500/40">
            <p>
              OPTYP and its affiliates shall not be held liable for any direct, indirect, or consequential damages resulting from the use or inability to use our services, 
              website, or content — including but not limited to data loss, business interruptions, or loss of opportunity.
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Affiliate & External Links -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-teal-400 font-bold text-2xl mb-4">8. Affiliate & External Links</h2>
          <p>
            OPTYP may partner with third-party affiliates for promotional or referral purposes. 
            Any commission or compensation received will not affect our objectivity or commitment to providing value.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-gray-400 text-sm">
            Users are responsible for verifying information before making any purchase through external links.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Force Majeure -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-teal-400 font-bold text-2xl mb-4">9. Force Majeure</h2>
          <p>
            OPTYP shall not be held liable for delays or service interruptions caused by events beyond our reasonable control, 
            including but not limited to internet outages, natural disasters, system failures, or cyber incidents.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Jurisdiction -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-teal-400 font-bold text-2xl mb-4">10. Jurisdiction & Legal Compliance</h2>
          <p>
            This Disclaimer shall be governed by the laws of <strong>India</strong>, in accordance with the IT Act (2000) and Consumer Protection (E-commerce) Rules (2020). 
            Any disputes shall fall under the jurisdiction of the courts of <strong>Hyderabad, Telangana</strong>.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Updates Clause -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-teal-400 font-bold text-2xl mb-4">11. Updates to This Disclaimer</h2>
          <p>
            OPTYP reserves the right to modify, update, or replace this Disclaimer at any time without prior notice. 
            Continued use of our website or services implies acceptance of the revised terms.
          </p>
        </section>

        <!-- Contact -->
        <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-500 to-green-500 text-white p-8 rounded-xl text-center shadow-xl">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Have Questions About This Disclaimer?</h2>
          <p class="mb-6">If you have any concerns or require clarifications regarding this Disclaimer, feel free to reach out to our support team.</p>
          <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:info@optyp.com" class="underline hover:text-gray-200">info@optyp.com</a></p>
          <p><strong>Contact Page:</strong> <a href="/contact/" class="underline hover:text-gray-200">Visit Our Contact Page</a></p>
        </section>

      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Structured Data for SEO -->
  <script type="application/ld+json">
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "WebPage",
    "name": "Disclaimer - OPTYP",
    "url": "https://optyp.github.io/disclaimer/",
    "description": "Official Disclaimer outlining OPTYP’s service limitations, liability terms, third-party link policies, and jurisdiction information.",
    "publisher": {
      "@type": "Organization",
      "name": "OPTYP",
      "url": "https://optyp.github.io",
      "logo": {
        "@type": "ImageObject",
        "url": "https://optyp.github.io/images/logo.svg"
      },
      "contactPoint": {
        "@type": "ContactPoint",
        "email": "info@optyp.com",
        "contactType": "Customer Support",
        "availableLanguage": ["English"]
      }
    },
    "inLanguage": "en"
  }
  </script>

  <style>
    .glass-box {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      border: 1px solid rgba(20,184,166,0.4);
      border-radius: 1rem;
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
    }
    article a {
      color: #5eead4;
      transition: color 0.3s ease;
    }
    article a:hover {
      color: #86efac;
    }
    @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
      * {
        animation-duration: 0ms !important;
        transition-duration: 0ms !important;
      }
    }
  </style>
</Layout>
